1. terninal config
1.1 install iTerm2
1.2 vim 
    $ cd solarized 
    $ cd vim-colors-solarized/colors 
    $ mkdir -p ~/.vim/colors 
    $ cp solarized.vim ~/.vim/colors/ 
    $ vi ~/.vimrc syntax enable set background=dark colorscheme solarized  (ru'guo如果如果vimrc文件，创建)
 1.3 ls
    $ vi ~/.bash_profile export CLICOLOR=1
      source ~/.bash_profile
      
2.install wget
  2.1 install brew()
  2.2 chown the brew's owner to root
  2.3 brew search/install wget

3.change terninal header
  3.1 vim /etc/bashrc
  3.2 chang W to w to shwo current work dir
  3.3 rm u to remove the user name
  3.4 chown hostname: sudo scutil --set HostName newname 
